---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Contact Us"
description: "Get a free quote from CNO Pole Barns. Call (248) 625-2334 or fill out our contact form. Serving Rochester Hills, Clarkston, Oakland County, and Southeast Michigan."
permalink: /contact/
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--gold);">Contact Us</span>
    <h1>Let's Build Something Great</h1>
    <p>Get a free, no-obligation estimate for your next project. We'd love to hear from you.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-info fade-up">
        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
        <p>Whether you're planning a new pole barn, need a garage, or want to discuss a barndominium — we're here to help. Call us directly or fill out the form and we'll get back to you within one business day.</p>
        <div class="contact-detail">
          <div class="contact-detail-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Phone</h4>
            <p><a href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">{{ site.phone }}</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-detail">
          <div class="contact-detail-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Address</h4>
            <p>{{ site.address.street }}<br>{{ site.address.city }}, {{ site.address.state }} {{ site.address.zip }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-detail">
          <div class="contact-detail-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Hours</h4>
            <p>Monday – Saturday<br>8:30 AM – 7:00 PM</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-detail">
          <div class="contact-detail-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Email</h4>
            <p><a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-form fade-up">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Request a Free Quote</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--gray-500); margin-bottom: 28px; font-size: 0.9375rem;">Fill out the form below and we'll get back to you within one business day.</p>
        <form>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="firstName">First Name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" required placeholder="John">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="lastName">Last Name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" required placeholder="Doe">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email *</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="john@example.com">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone">Phone *</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required placeholder="(248) 555-1234">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="projectType">Project Type</label>
            <select id="projectType" name="projectType">
              <option value="">Select a project type...</option>
              {% for service in collections.services %}
              <option value="{{ service.data.title | lower }}">{{ service.data.title }}</option>
              {% endfor %}
              <option value="other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="location">Project Location (City/Township)</label>
            <input type="text" id="location" name="location" placeholder="Rochester Hills, MI">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Tell Us About Your Project</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Describe your project — size, purpose, timeline, budget range, or any other details."></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="form-submit">Send Quote Request</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
